```
# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者買賣嗰陣，為咗防止虧損進一步擴大，而及時賣出資產或者平倉；亦引申為及時放棄某樣嘢以免損失更多（量詞：個）
eng:to stop loss; to cut one's losses; to sell off an asset to prevent further loss
<eg>
yue:隻股票跌到咁，都係盡早止蝕好啲。 (zek3 gu2 piu3 dit3 dou3 gam3, dou1 hai6 zeon6 zou2 zi2 sik6 hou2 di1.)
eng:The stock has dropped so much, it's better to cut your losses early.

``` [end of text]


